Date: Fri, 27 Mar 2026 16:31:39 -0300
Subject: [PATCH] Fixes for OTP 29

 - use lists:filtermap/2 instead lists:zf/2
 - adopt try..catch instead catch

1: https://erlang.org/download//OTP-29.0-rc1.README

Upstream-Status: Submitted [https://github.com/hawk/lux/pull/59]
---
